1. *Reakcija* je bila veoma brza. (The *reaction* was very fast.)
2. Naša *reakcija* nije bila dovoljno jaka da izazove promenu. (Our *reaction* was not strong enough to cause a change.)
3. Političari se često bore za *reakciju* javnosti. (Politicians often fight for a *reaction* from the public.)
4. Posmatrali smo *reakciju* hemijske reakcije. (We observed the *reaction* of a chemical reaction.)
5. Njegova *reakcija* na vest bila je iznenađujuća. (His *reaction* to the news was surprising.)
6. Nije mi se svidela *reakcija* na moj predlog. (I didn't like the *reaction* to my proposal.)
7. *Reakcija* mu je bila brza i precizna. (His *reaction* was quick and precise.)
8. Telo ima *reakciju* na stres. (The body has a *reaction* to stress.)
9. Upotreba *reakcije* u hemiji je veoma važna. (The use of *reaction* in chemistry is very important.)
10. Nismo očekivali takvu *reakciju* na našu akciju. (We didn't expect such a *reaction* to our action.)